"{\"event\":\"job.completed\",\"jobId\":\"ccc253e7-51fa-4169-bfc7-c45c4428e40e\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-23T07:56:15.960Z\",\"status\":\"completed\",\"result\":{\"data\":[\"v0.2\",{\"title\":\"Comment analysis\",\"description\":\"Analysis of comments\",\"topics\":[{\"id\":\"06434151-7f9f-4467-9d71-87a429359df8\",\"title\":\"AI in Society\",\"description\":\"AI in Society\",\"summary\":\"The discussion around 'AI in Society' highlights concerns about its impact on privacy, surveillance, education, and the workforce. Key themes include privacy risks from AI systems like Amazon and Google's constant data tracking, and reduced social interactions due to AI imposition. Concerns are also raised about AI's predictive capabilities affecting mental health and the need for worker awareness when AI evaluates performance. In education and workforce, there's debate over AI's role in schools and its potential to displace jobs without adequate retraining opportunities. AI’s reliability is questioned due to its frequent errors. Overall, participants express apprehension over AI's reach and the necessity for responsible integration and oversight.\",\"subtopics\":[{\"id\":\"c7316a61-0fac-4323-b219-dccbfb2c30da\",\"title\":\"Privacy & Surveillance\",\"description\":\"Privacy & Surveillance\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"90cff4f7-2ae9-48de-a8cc-62156b77b0a9\",\"title\":\"AI systems pose privacy risks due to constant data monitoring and tracking capabilities.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"a155eec9-46e5-4739-b68f-c582212a7153\",\"text\":\"I can guarantee that it's connected into, into the network. Hm. And they, they probably know the location of it, your cell phone.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"77da7ebd-00da-4790-a1be-d95e5f494de9\",\"sourceId\":\"48784da4-b563-4209-9130-31331782f2f6\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":32,\"endIdx\":161}]}}],\"number\":15,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"74c01dbd-e21f-48aa-8b87-a1c187d56bc5\",\"title\":\"AI systems like those from Amazon or Google pose privacy risks because they are always listening.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"0638d77a-e4dc-4a84-b8dc-520bd752dfaa\",\"text\":\"protecting yourself is key by shutting down stuff that's on Amazon or Google or whatever because it's always listening\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"baff26f1-651f-4086-bf74-8803afa98471\",\"sourceId\":\"3d214790-626b-487d-8870-8be56c604f5b\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":187,\"endIdx\":305}]}}],\"number\":16,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"c22ac29f-0cc2-4b8d-a0db-71d149574acd\",\"title\":\"Failing to protect personal data results in exposure to privacy risks.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"a2bab8f2-5f29-4dc2-8eb6-6aa516ba9ab9\",\"text\":\"when you're throwing data out there and you're not protecting yourself, it, it, it can, it's all exposed\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"3ebfcf1b-7947-497f-a9e0-4dd3572e7ca9\",\"sourceId\":\"3d214790-626b-487d-8870-8be56c604f5b\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":352,\"endIdx\":456}]}}],\"number\":17,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"9a0237f7-fcf2-4338-a8a5-c12f9da66b33\",\"title\":\"AI is often imposed on consumers and reduces perceived social needs.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"314fffe0-1f08-4d8b-a4fd-80f3968de730\",\"text\":\"It's forced on us. Um-hum. Yes. Yes.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"f8a740bc-8305-42ce-af00-f1461a413271\",\"sourceId\":\"e956a6b4-8a52-4b14-946f-80633825b384\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":135,\"endIdx\":171}]}}],\"number\":18,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"3d8d11eb-2ba6-41f9-b872-146f3520e4f0\",\"title\":\"AI like Alexa may reduce the perceived need for human social interactions.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"b78295b8-2a74-4efe-8e98-f1aff20b51e4\",\"text\":\"And with her, maybe you don't need as many friends.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"25f54498-b00b-48b3-97c0-73be94c7e2d2\",\"sourceId\":\"91ac77a9-cb3c-49ac-af50-2a04a3d9a9e5\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":31,\"endIdx\":82}]}}],\"number\":19,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"77cf141d-f9a3-4c36-bea4-ddfea0f02682\",\"title\":\"AI's predictive capabilities raise concerns about mental health and require awareness.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"513cdc1e-ba34-4875-994e-03823d87e1fe\",\"text\":\"It doesn't read tone and it doesn't read emotion, but the more that you use it, it's literally meant to predict you, and you can find it if you pay attention to it, but it does require a level of awareness, which has me worried about mental health.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"7f443aef-321e-478b-956a-e76e7e333e77\",\"sourceId\":\"e407185b-e006-4894-975c-eb712765ae32\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":248}]}}],\"number\":20,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"1d5a4a02-df43-4af5-911c-533e4bf94acd\",\"title\":\"Workers should have the right to know when AI is used to evaluate their performance.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"e23e9561-e3e2-4d5c-b89f-c7c12903c78c\",\"text\":\"workers should have the right to know when AI is being used to evaluate their performance and productivity.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"85ec5e3e-3590-4cee-bd1e-cf054d9359dd\",\"sourceId\":\"45e06c0e-dfa0-4c80-ab59-b95f771037b3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":335,\"endIdx\":442}]}}],\"number\":21,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"80c59fe2-eb17-401e-ae7a-e925019c2f11\",\"title\":\"Education & Workforce\",\"description\":\"Education & Workforce\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"127aca27-e563-4944-9234-27869467317a\",\"title\":\"AI's impact on jobs requires companies to provide training and create new job opportunities for affected workers.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"e1a2df7d-b50e-4eda-9023-a265b0c2ef59\",\"text\":\"if they're not gonna be willing to train people of the jobs that they're taking away, then they don't belong in that area.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"42a91eba-6430-44fa-a84f-dca56025539b\",\"sourceId\":\"91afb219-1e13-4990-a903-366aabea5244\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":126,\"endIdx\":248}]}}],\"number\":22,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"f96466c8-855e-40b5-a6ec-469d94e6e254\",\"title\":\"AI should create new job opportunities rather than just eliminating existing jobs\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"2fefeec6-fbdd-4f7b-bd4f-def9d5225c63\",\"text\":\"I don't build AI to take jobs. [...] you need to be able to provide another way of, of earning for that person as well.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"744f6b4e-b959-45e4-802e-996164214773\",\"sourceId\":\"cc51a3fa-2780-46d0-9301-fa64265f57c7\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":118}]}}],\"number\":23,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"ae353d89-b5c2-4cfe-9ea6-189e70b4a087\",\"title\":\"AI should be integrated into education, but there are differing opinions on its implementation in schools.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"bab1c2df-2b76-47dc-9974-a2cf1929df56\",\"text\":\"people are disagreeing on AI should be part of every student's education.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"345bf4a4-2a69-4442-96b7-01b3bd277555\",\"sourceId\":\"7d2290d1-3093-480d-816d-5d5e17c058e0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":63,\"endIdx\":136}]}}],\"number\":24,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"060f85b1-fce6-4d27-bab7-79003eded428\",\"title\":\"Current AI technologies are perceived as unreliable and often make mistakes.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"67b4938c-0584-4b19-9c94-f5e0f0252626\",\"text\":\"It's BS. It lies to you a lot. OK, I catch it on a daily basis.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"858087f1-f848-49bf-a43c-8dfcef0d9792\",\"sourceId\":\"88db7dff-2f24-42ff-abf0-13874fbad99a\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":291,\"endIdx\":354}]}}],\"number\":25,\"similarClaims\":[]}]}],\"topicColor\":\"blueSky\"},{\"id\":\"32897895-9b7a-4bf1-92fe-fcd6c5d3b8e1\",\"title\":\"Data Centers Impact\",\"description\":\"Data Centers Impact\",\"summary\":\"The discussion around data centers highlights significant concerns under two primary themes: community displacement and environmental impact. Community displacement issues arise from claims that data centers prioritize industrial needs over community welfare, often leading to resource conflicts, particularly water. Additionally, the economic benefits to local communities are questioned, as job creation post-construction is minimal. On the environmental front, data centers are criticized for their substantial resource consumption, impacting local water and electricity supplies, and contributing to temperature increases. Calls for transparency, regulation, and compensation for environmental damage are prevalent, underscoring the need for responsible planning and accountability. Overall, these centers are seen as powerful entities with far-reaching implications beyond their immediate footprint.\",\"subtopics\":[{\"id\":\"77f7556c-ebfa-4db8-9aec-8e5f8624ae87\",\"title\":\"Environmental Impact\",\"description\":\"Environmental Impact\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"4485f858-2e57-436c-9e74-b690c3aa8c85\",\"title\":\"Data centers have a significant environmental impact due to their resource consumption, including energy and water.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"3f94df1a-6b39-4cc0-9787-c0db4faa92be\",\"text\":\"Then the more data centers we have to build, and that's where I come from. I'm about the environment.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"02db5d43-80c9-4f89-8659-40908acdc2d5\",\"sourceId\":\"b1f90676-b762-4121-8261-5285e3819af0\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":213,\"endIdx\":314}]}}],\"number\":1,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"2c276621-a934-4c1e-a55e-730e9eec669a\",\"title\":\"AI data centers consume excessive energy that impacts local resources.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"3b83a57c-3bcf-4d47-adda-9527061e3fc0\",\"text\":\"some of the AI centers are powering, they're using up enough energy to power 100,000 homes at a time\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"55ed1811-c40e-46e1-85be-b0a237ef4231\",\"sourceId\":\"5884a1ca-8530-465b-916c-6f4b3c427417\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":65,\"endIdx\":165}]}}],\"number\":2,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"9d244239-adb5-41bd-b0ca-89603ab87473\",\"title\":\"Data centers heavily impact water and electricity resources.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"fb42b81b-5941-4566-8a14-7fec5ad87b27\",\"text\":\"What resources are we talking about using as far as water and electricity? Those seem to be the top two commodities that are discussed, and those have me deeply alarmed.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"2b1c3e0f-750c-43c3-b625-889e6e5730c2\",\"sourceId\":\"d3dd1fa9-c5b7-40b2-a449-f4a9b4fe5802\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":274,\"endIdx\":443}]}}],\"number\":3,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"9195d017-4740-461c-9c35-20600f793c53\",\"title\":\"The environmental heat and temperature increases around data centers need consideration due to their impact on local climates.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"fed46e22-50eb-4275-8b79-f342c3222e55\",\"text\":\"And then the heat that is being put out into the atmosphere, where is it going?\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"7f46737d-8ae3-4608-a603-e59a9cb0a5db\",\"sourceId\":\"e036edc2-6de2-41fe-a826-c8b164b98a0b\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":46,\"endIdx\":125}]}}],\"number\":4,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"e8a4ef9e-afde-4fbb-9a6b-c0a45c67ef0a\",\"title\":\"Data centers increase local temperatures, impacting the environment.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"e53e5af1-fa4c-4160-81be-52fc528fa1bc\",\"text\":\"the temperature around the data center rises from 2 to 16 degrees, depending upon the size of the data center\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"4d53bf97-105f-4e1e-80d0-643cc931679b\",\"sourceId\":\"74732ca3-9d98-409b-a8f3-181313b1e8a3\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":64,\"endIdx\":173}]}}],\"number\":5,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"946ec567-fdd6-4c61-be75-05a8987fbe4c\",\"title\":\"Data centers should report their resource usage, such as electricity, to promote transparency and accountability.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"15416a18-d0be-464b-add7-e04940d426c5\",\"text\":\"Oregon currently requires uh large data centers to report their water use. They should also have to report how much electricity they consume.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"91ee2f72-6f92-4749-bcfc-23c18257db1a\",\"sourceId\":\"f658d7c2-6db3-46b3-bebb-03314b072abb\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":39,\"endIdx\":180}]}}],\"number\":6,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"cc0b054e-a96b-4bba-a116-ae478c4e077d\",\"title\":\"Data centers should not be located in water-rich areas because of resource conservation concerns.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"e750a925-3097-41bd-8481-6c4b230d352e\",\"text\":\"And where are they going to want to put data centers? They're going to want to put data centers where they can get the water.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"59e049da-3bae-4c5e-ae96-9da865058993\",\"sourceId\":\"59ed3e8b-d3bc-4310-83d1-fa2c51df3c4b\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":259,\"endIdx\":384}]}}],\"number\":7,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"f55c96dd-2813-4404-9d70-18f0a18cb746\",\"title\":\"Regulation of data centers is necessary before construction to address environmental and resource concerns.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"54f926f9-73b4-4449-8b85-c06535cb497a\",\"text\":\"I would like to see legislation in place before we get the data centers.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"3dc30217-6589-4426-80c1-dddb6575e9a3\",\"sourceId\":\"2d1a624c-ff71-40a3-b4c6-91978d984dda\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":72}]}}],\"number\":8,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"7db8efc8-431d-46ce-8b44-4c9947e157b1\",\"title\":\"Data center capacity is equated with power and control, indicating broader implications beyond environmental issues.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"81b3ad90-4e96-4424-be4e-0b0157bc983f\",\"text\":\"He who has the most data center capacity has the most power.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"1f32affc-05e3-4b3c-8f7e-5b0325d2242e\",\"sourceId\":\"9a69bc19-55ce-4a0a-9b45-e8025f65e3f0\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":190,\"endIdx\":250}]}}],\"number\":9,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"4c73124d-63e3-490b-a10f-8494bcb64880\",\"title\":\"Community Displacement\",\"description\":\"Community Displacement\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"a6c8fcc2-3111-4467-9863-80bab9b5cea1\",\"title\":\"Data centers prioritize industrial needs over community welfare and access to resources.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"d3d3ad1c-e6d4-42a2-b9f4-952c3ce9cda9\",\"text\":\"there are places that are being told, Lake Tahoe, for instance, 30% of their population is being told you have so.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"648e6a0d-01c0-48f2-bd18-c37e16abd2e7\",\"sourceId\":\"5884a1ca-8530-465b-916c-6f4b3c427417\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":182,\"endIdx\":296}]}}],\"number\":10,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"35564e59-6441-4c29-88f6-5a5e7780237a\",\"title\":\"Data centers should not prioritize industrial needs over community welfare.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"b0953f43-48e6-4d6c-b070-cc6305794bf0\",\"text\":\"The farmers are gonna have to move because they don't have the water and the farmers are going against.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"ab9d9cfa-46c6-4b5f-bf05-3026e7b3caa5\",\"sourceId\":\"513db2e7-3181-4606-9d4c-54364724fa3c\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":112,\"endIdx\":215}]}}],\"number\":11,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"9bb1fa27-062f-4814-a699-a219904f6ced\",\"title\":\"Data centers prioritize industrial needs over community access to water.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"da47ebd6-0f30-48a9-86d1-cd6b64c79e79\",\"text\":\"Our water is under attack, is how I feel. That's my concern. My concern is the next 7 generations, not just for my people, not just for indigenous people, but for all people.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"3a9a152b-9596-4887-a88e-ade25e8739fe\",\"sourceId\":\"466e0ff1-39ed-476d-9fdf-ee14898bdc34\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":174}]}}],\"number\":12,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"41d55d55-e475-4835-91a6-c7bab41ba236\",\"title\":\"Data centers should compensate communities for environmental damage caused by their operations.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"086f15d9-ff7d-48e1-9a74-d53fdcbac64b\",\"text\":\"Now you owe the whole community hundreds of millions of dollars to fix what you've done.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"ce2d27f2-4136-40ac-aaf6-5f131c8c46b0\",\"sourceId\":\"e6a34dab-b635-4686-adba-5a714c523ec3\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":135,\"endIdx\":223}]}}],\"number\":13,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"2c3f129c-5689-4932-83ed-f6ef9f6262c3\",\"title\":\"Data centers do not significantly boost local employment and mainly offer low-skill jobs post-construction.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"d792e8af-be7c-4a45-8643-812a7b77bb8d\",\"text\":\"They bring in a construction team to build the data center, and when they're done, then they roll out and they, they hire a few janitorial staff and a few, uh, technicians to swap out hard drives and motherboards.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"e4042ceb-cfa2-48a1-8ead-71b2e9f20257\",\"sourceId\":\"9d948141-35a8-40cb-953a-f2f29301625a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":45,\"endIdx\":258}]}}],\"number\":14,\"similarClaims\":[]}]}],\"topicColor\":\"brown\"},{\"id\":\"55fb3f0a-9046-40f8-98c3-2214ba8aa237\",\"title\":\"AI Funding & Accountability\",\"description\":\"AI Funding & Accountability\",\"summary\":\"The discussion on 'AI Funding & Accountability' centers on the financial and operational responsibilities of AI corporations. Key themes include corporate responsibility for self-financing without public subsidies, emphasizing the expectation that profitable AI companies should independently support infrastructure and operational expenses. Assertions suggest that these corporations must fully mitigate negative impacts, ensuring they cause no harm to communities. Furthermore, there's a perspective that regulatory responsibilities are increasingly being transferred to businesses themselves. Although the 'Environmental Costs' subtopic lacks specific claims, the topic underscores the necessity for AI firms to bear full accountability, both financially and operationally, in their ventures.\",\"subtopics\":[{\"id\":\"a72e5209-b8bd-47de-bbed-27c6c5e06a26\",\"title\":\"Corporate Responsibility\",\"description\":\"Corporate Responsibility\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"066828f3-c49f-4c3e-967e-d5d82355129c\",\"title\":\"AI corporations should finance their own infrastructure and operational costs without public funding or subsidies.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"7eb29eb2-1a53-45ba-a797-1e7feeda4c5c\",\"text\":\"AI is expensive and they should be paying their own bills. These are billionaires running.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"614ed018-33e1-43db-b799-d83bb2812236\",\"sourceId\":\"c3398fff-12bd-4fba-a652-e8c64dbe584a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":90}]}}],\"number\":26,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"65387ac9-b3da-4fdd-9972-6b3af0521d87\",\"title\":\"AI companies should cover operational costs as part of doing business\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"1220d7ab-1dd2-47cc-9682-30678202f7d7\",\"text\":\"This should be part of the cost of doing business. AI is very expensive to run.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"22ef6cf1-e3ad-49b0-9bfd-1ec078940279\",\"sourceId\":\"33260714-b117-4560-9611-7db039df55ab\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":152,\"endIdx\":231}]}}],\"number\":27,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"916e0763-b540-4bbc-ae7f-8aee4cac08c6\",\"title\":\"AI corporations should pay for their own operational expenses without public funding or subsidies.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"4d13d329-11fc-454f-95e1-8bb5455fb6b3\",\"text\":\"So why are they asking other people to pay their business bills?\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"17766ce0-70eb-495e-9ac3-a205a833a9bf\",\"sourceId\":\"242ab715-599a-4ff6-afd2-f81df78bc44c\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":64}]}}],\"number\":28,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"b2c957d5-c8f2-4f7f-9ba8-3e637939d2ed\",\"title\":\"AI corporations should financially support their infrastructure costs without public subsidies.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"44b4a46a-b72b-4c14-b70d-1a89a132691a\",\"text\":\"These companies need to pay their own damn bills.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"1f9ce425-542a-4687-93ad-1a4a8daa5ec1\",\"sourceId\":\"00ca8917-26b7-4616-b126-4eb7bf2d5751\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":49}]}}],\"number\":29,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"1dedf2a5-1920-49bc-a18f-380661db7940\",\"title\":\"AI corporations should be financially independent and cover their own operational expenses.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"de37fd20-b3e4-4f7a-b393-4e62f7adb8ea\",\"text\":\"And the corporations need to pay their own bills. I mean, if it's, if it's really a, a powerhouse of, of, uh, profitability, then they should be able to pay their own bills with that profit,\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"60ba1eb7-0264-4ece-8103-30c03dc45c29\",\"sourceId\":\"41617f65-c470-4e1a-87fa-e953d9fc2675\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":190}]}}],\"number\":30,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"3377f333-26c6-4f96-af89-fd444be85f0f\",\"title\":\"AI corporations should fully contain their impact to prevent harm.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"4f9408ff-3abe-4263-92f0-7d17ffbf6870\",\"text\":\"If you, if, if you wanna bring it here, show us that you're 100% contained and you don't, you won't do anything to, to harm what's around us or us together.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"7edee603-6efd-4400-91c0-4ee3f03cc105\",\"sourceId\":\"2c99fa1a-2073-4627-bfb0-dde53bc387af\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":155}]}}],\"number\":31,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"b2b6148e-41fb-4764-b46b-5ae2eafdf2a8\",\"title\":\"Regulation of AI is becoming the responsibility of businesses.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"3297f8db-f0fa-4a32-beca-c0ba0518346b\",\"text\":\"And I think to his point, yes, the burden of regulation now falls on us.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"e187a69e-ed1c-42e5-b636-3bef3780e693\",\"sourceId\":\"8c65f465-f5f8-4408-adb5-e511d4677d87\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":335,\"endIdx\":407}]}}],\"number\":32,\"similarClaims\":[]}]}],\"topicColor\":\"greenLeaf\"},{\"id\":\"57b2754c-2c62-4079-8d87-8ec94a7aeca5\",\"title\":\"Public Consultation & Engagement\",\"description\":\"Public Consultation & Engagement\",\"summary\":\"Public Consultation & Engagement highlights the critical role of civic participation in enhancing democratic decision-making, especially in AI policy development. Citizen assemblies are praised for making informed recommendations, fostering deliberative democracy, and improving decision-making processes. However, concerns are raised about inadequate public consultation, where community voices are often sidelined before agreements are finalized. This exclusion leads to shortcomings in inclusivity in decision-making. Additionally, the rapid pace of AI development poses a challenge, with regulatory frameworks struggling to keep up, causing gaps in effective governance. Overall, the discussion emphasizes the need for more structured and inclusive public consultation mechanisms to address these issues effectively.\",\"subtopics\":[{\"id\":\"9cf94b1c-cbef-48ac-8b43-6d24d9a93874\",\"title\":\"Civic Participation\",\"description\":\"Civic Participation\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"8cca840c-80b2-4f3b-b596-66b028d423d5\",\"title\":\"Citizen assemblies and community engagements enhance democratic decision-making and provide informed AI policy recommendations.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"620c6c81-1265-411d-b208-9b41e1143b8f\",\"text\":\"They'll be educated on information about AI and then we'll come together in groups to deliberate and come up with recommendations that would then go to political bodies or or appropriate folks.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"40be2f49-a7fc-49b8-9f1c-a4ef4f505e7a\",\"sourceId\":\"e614532e-0a45-4508-8079-8aacd732b031\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":53,\"endIdx\":246}]}}],\"number\":33,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"36ecfddf-a5e2-4b75-bf8f-6ee2fb896263\",\"title\":\"Community engagements and citizen assemblies enhance democratic practices.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"82f09aaf-4f87-4ea6-9dc9-2ba0d5c915fb\",\"text\":\"For us to be engaging people in, in civic discussion and deliberative democracy.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"208b2252-3070-4c96-a670-afa401bd509b\",\"sourceId\":\"a1ee15ac-9318-4226-bb5d-ea4017048667\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":80}]}}],\"number\":34,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"a7d9112e-521d-49b6-9c37-191c0bb81928\",\"title\":\"Citizen engagement enhances decision-making processes.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"f64a93c6-cf58-408f-baee-31c6176f815e\",\"text\":\"What we do have is tell us what you think and we will consider it in our decision making, which is a huge leap forward\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"04dd47a7-428f-4f51-97f2-30638d8615d4\",\"sourceId\":\"5dd7bdfd-4cb5-448a-be1e-8a7c1f28d4f0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":118}]}}],\"number\":35,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"4a3bc50f-fa57-4142-bc86-97d8e51fde07\",\"title\":\"Public consultation is often inadequate or absent in AI implementation and community decision-making processes are sidelined before finalizing deals.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"e6b18cec-b12e-40ab-89e0-6b2d610e37bd\",\"text\":\"We weren't asked about it. We weren't given a choice.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"6f62592c-7dd6-4a75-a077-5c38989f71bd\",\"sourceId\":\"4300cb0c-d0ed-415c-b322-fbb3b2d363fd\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":94,\"endIdx\":147}]}}],\"number\":36,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"ccf8fd0b-e554-4b2c-98ef-64d33cc35836\",\"title\":\"Communities are often excluded from discussions before deals are finalized.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"53c30222-2acd-4496-9c22-ca7b2b8ff0e7\",\"text\":\"what we're hearing is there's too many times that they come in, the deal is done before the community even gets to talk about it.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"364ed49b-c3b7-4338-887d-87e5b96d2df0\",\"sourceId\":\"c60fd74b-1afb-4829-9229-2f6a81fe6396\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":109,\"endIdx\":238}]}}],\"number\":37,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"5054e7db-b6a4-4b7b-86bf-78d03dfc0ecf\",\"title\":\"The pace of AI development outpaces regulatory frameworks, challenging the ability to keep up with changes.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"541222ca-d77e-49c4-b046-a92a0e9efa56\",\"text\":\"Entrepreneurs don't move at the speed of government, we move at the speed of business. But with everything that's going on, it really feels like even us, we just cannot keep up with everything that is going on.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"0b82091d-6cdf-4099-abe3-12a26fab3005\",\"sourceId\":\"8c65f465-f5f8-4408-adb5-e511d4677d87\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":124,\"endIdx\":334}]}}],\"number\":38,\"similarClaims\":[]}]}],\"topicColor\":\"purple\"}],\"sources\":[{\"id\":\"c3398fff-12bd-4fba-a652-e8c64dbe584a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"AI is expensive and they should be paying their own bills. These are billionaires running. Yes. Yeah, they should be paying their own bills for it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c5e41ea3-bb31-45a5-a7d0-8e65c1ef0667\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Come sit with us at the table. One of them's a trillionaire.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a88c9c8e-8f26-4ccc-907c-3a757e472de9\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Almost. Good. You're talking about Elon? Yeah. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b34e2722-565d-4386-b342-52067c927cfd\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"All right, we're just doing some introductions if you'd like to introduce yourself. I'm Elena and I'm 15 years old and I'm here with my mom. This is my sister. She's Zyla.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0977689f-ac1a-4430-82a6-53bf80ba0d41\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm. Nice to meet you, Zyla.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6c68734f-1d7e-4c61-8322-72aa77bc1592\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Hi, my name is Melinda Billy. I'm from Yakama Nation, descendant of Warm Springs, um, reservation, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0d369bb5-9851-46ab-9d53-49bd3db1bf6e\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm a water activist.\"}]},{\"id\":\"92a1e336-07af-4672-8206-d91397cdbbba\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And uh thank you. I'm here on behalf of not just my people and our treaty rights, but all people in Mother Earth.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6521abdc-2c7d-4866-bee8-e57db5574c6b\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, I just would like to know what the plans are and what to expect and what to report back to my\"}]},{\"id\":\"6fe75292-77f5-4dfc-8d13-d33d155bd8f1\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"people.\"}]},{\"id\":\"50cae8c9-78f0-408e-8073-5cac2e5400f9\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK. I don't know that we'll have any plans. There's no project that we're here to talk about. We're here to gather information from you about your hopes for AI or your concerns about AI and things related to it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"763282a5-0e62-4767-8a60-d5de255446b7\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"We're not here to perpetuate. Right. Other than,\"}]},{\"id\":\"901302d9-2295-4b9b-b09e-ce8b46de9809\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The process of trying to get people in Central Oregon, all of us to get better perspective and get a handle on.\"}]},{\"id\":\"77d5cff7-5e91-4d9c-9370-72f2c9936652\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The broader subject, including the very special specific things that folks are concerned about.\"}]},{\"id\":\"038f022d-0c8d-4fd9-8b59-027291706450\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Or you know, have interest in an opportunity.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9b07684f-d864-45cf-b380-2911dfc811ca\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, um, today we've done our introductions. I'm gonna tell you a little bit about an open poll that we've been running and the, um, kind of multi-stage process that COCAP is going through to gather, um, community input. Then, um, most of our time will be spent in a discussion where you'll be sharing, um, your values and trade-offs, concerns, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4453c313-569a-4e4f-b25a-9f0351ab45cd\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Your perspective on AI and then we'll wrap things up, OK?\"}]},{\"id\":\"b7d9aa6c-3d2d-43ed-a4dc-f7b33138b18b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, in this discussion, we want everybody to share, especially your personal perspective, um, and Melinda, I can send you the slides later if that's easier. I mean, you're welcome to take pictures if you want, but, um, yep, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a5d962ad-b0d0-4a97-99d3-52176f9094fe\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Is just share your, your own experiences and um feel free to, you know, we don't want anything to get combative, but I don't and I don't think we will, but you know if if there's a perspective that's different than yours, feel free to share yours as yours and you know because we wanna gather the breadth of uh perspectives on things and um please feel comfortable sharing your thoughts, everybody.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d1d3c8ea-321f-4684-9ec4-a6c5af704a11\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If you want to, no pressure.\"}]},{\"id\":\"3ee09378-da07-471c-b47b-30dbd8de5b4e\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, what COCAP is doing is a four-phase project on AI. The first is, um, what we call the open poll. The poll has been running since the end of April and will continue probably through the end of June. Have any of you seen or taken the poll?\"}]},{\"id\":\"0e173abe-5e4a-4ec2-886d-1daffa098666\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think, is that\"}]},{\"id\":\"663e5734-00a6-482c-83a4-cf46eb2a9171\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"the, um, what's the name of the, in, within the original COCAP blurb. Um-hum. There was a,\"}]},{\"id\":\"400c0939-1568-4b01-8591-48d8a7baf13a\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"a\"}]},{\"id\":\"89a37b2a-f9cd-4f45-9985-3b93c9385cc9\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yes, it said Bloom Project. OK, yep, so that was the open poll, and it's a little different than a typical survey in that it lists statements and you choose to agree, disagree, or to skip that statement. You also have the option to add your own statements for other people to to vote on. OK. The goal of the poll is to get a breadth of input.\"}]},{\"id\":\"8c90216b-4ee7-49f0-bf2c-438fefc53fe0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Not necessarily a lot of depth, but you know, to get general perspectives from um a wider group of people.\"}]},{\"id\":\"928e0291-b19a-4a06-97d1-429fe34ca87d\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Now is this strictly on AI or is this on, on data centers.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ca2acef3-54c0-4526-b1fc-58465c6b47f2\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It's on AI, but as, you know, we've already seen the whole data center discussion is there. It's sort of a, a Venn diagram, right?\"}]},{\"id\":\"4de100af-c926-4af2-8242-4be1f38d4825\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, so it's not specifically about data centers, it's about AI in general, including the hardware impacts and, you know, the software impacts and the societal impacts and so forth, all aspects, yes, all right, we're trying to make it at the poll level as broad as possible.\"}]},{\"id\":\"157b1201-13c3-4ec5-beb3-f8664fd3d75b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"To gather lots of different perspectives\"}]},{\"id\":\"f5409ae3-f285-489f-bc26-34b058139d99\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"with the goal of getting to a point for the assembly\"}]},{\"id\":\"209d140b-35df-4c03-8eca-ea0a9155c2c0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"correct, so the second step is what we're doing here, community conversations all around the region where we'll have an opportunity to get a little deeper into those concerns. Those two points of information will funnel into what's called a citizens assembly.\"}]},{\"id\":\"3790ae6b-e67d-4b29-aaad-6b14ba6935c5\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Which we'll be holding in December and a citizens assembly is a gathering of folks, uh, probably about 40 people who will be selected as demographically and politically representative of the region.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e614532e-0a45-4508-8079-8aacd732b031\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And those people will come together for 2, 2.5 days. They'll be educated on information about AI and then we'll come together in groups to deliberate and come up with recommendations that would then go to political bodies or or appropriate folks.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a7711f29-7648-471f-acd5-3c499c1c3aa2\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But because AI is such a big topic, part of our goal with the open poll and the community conversations is to find kind of the highest priority pieces of AI.\"}]},{\"id\":\"44f4a2be-1757-4766-a629-609e7a4dd5c3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"To do that really in-depth discussion rather than, you know, let's create policy for AI that's kind of big, you know, we may end up having the citizens assembly be about AI and mental health or AI and the workforce or AI and the elderly, absolutely.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6d795920-0f14-4e0e-98fc-5ecfd5b880cf\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So COCAP has done a citizens assembly in the past. 2 years ago, they ran a citizens assembly in Deschutes County on youth homelessness and so did this same thing. They didn't do the first steps. They went straight to the citizens assembly, brought together a group of representative folks. I think they had 30 representative folks, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9a9ce3f9-6f4e-4303-8388-4aaef0ddfb64\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Who came together for 3 days, learned all about youth homelessness from lots of different perspectives, ended up coming up with a list of, I think it was about 27 recommendations, um, and those recommendations went to.\"}]},{\"id\":\"36750263-7ed1-4b98-aadb-af4575670a9f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The city of Bend went to Deschutes County, went to the school district, went to some of the nonprofits, you know, whoever could actually do something about those particular recommendations, and you know, a portion of those recommendations are being incorporated into um what's being done in those entities and that's where we're planning on this going.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0b8b0213-94f3-49b6-9e80-33337b0eae72\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"By the time that we finish the process,\"}]},{\"id\":\"fe2caddf-1646-4cef-a005-9dbce95928fc\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK,\"}]},{\"id\":\"927a1fec-b516-4f0b-9d7b-8b1040c79a3f\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"who's\"}]},{\"id\":\"2d64c74c-b4a4-4795-85d5-3a04e8c582c4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"gonna be providing the education for the group? It'll depend on what slice of AI we end up talking about. So it will be um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"77a9d026-9d9b-4373-8d38-867889ad67ae\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"A broad spectrum of people who are knowledgeable about all, all sides of that issue because\"}]},{\"id\":\"0e0839c7-d366-41f2-a625-c6f71e5118db\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"it could be\"}]},{\"id\":\"672a0360-6087-4a53-b55a-8e53b3fd731f\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"easily\"}]},{\"id\":\"7b93ccf0-17be-4938-9afe-0503c1882f56\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"propagandized.\"}]},{\"id\":\"65b048e5-efae-434d-a71b-e1ee744ded2d\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Oh, of course, and that is not what this is about. So you know the intent, like if we do mental health, there will be mental health professionals and there will be AI people who, you know, work in the area of mental health and there will be researchers who do it, you know.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6ad5c60c-bc8e-42f6-909e-2fcde5c6e36c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Intention and very our mission is to bring together unbiased, no, unbiased isn't the right word because each of those will have their own bias, but a broad enough spectrum to provide an ultimately.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a33568b4-0529-48ae-b636-d139329849f8\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Neutral perspective for the people who are deliberating right the goal is to provide information, not propaganda. So a large part of what we'll be doing between now and then is identifying those, you know, who are those people and vetting them and preparing them and.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f5e63ed9-0556-4a3f-8022-52dab44851d0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And, um, so\"}]},{\"id\":\"e653175b-21a9-46a9-9b51-3ca7ab184699\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"if\"}]},{\"id\":\"5d808abc-5f0e-4556-a7b4-6da3f5986bb5\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I were running for office, this is something that I might keep track of for future references.\"}]},{\"id\":\"62156c6c-e536-4c44-9ea3-753aa5f696fd\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah. Absolutely. And we do have a lot of, in fact, I would say most of the representatives regionally are at least aware of CAP and, and the work that we're doing.\"}]},{\"id\":