h, and it sort of, sort of reinforces the point of why we're here, and that is so we can know even what the questions need to be, to, to be able to know how to help.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e5879193-ebc4-42e4-8e82-0b2b235d3c7b\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Meet the cause, which is us getting our arms around this, including definitions, including context, including all of those things. So.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cc572a57-4d99-4629-909d-e31c8b091017\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, and to the point of capturing what I, the point I think she's trying to make.\"}]},{\"id\":\"eb90da20-ed43-4afe-b5a1-82fb52ae39d0\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think part of your concern is,\"}]},{\"id\":\"5e38fcaa-0665-4335-aa54-1d0d34efebce\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Are there artists who are not being paid for the content that went into this presentation, or any presentation?\"}]},{\"id\":\"2b2b7177-d3aa-4d1b-8bff-dde24d5cc6ad\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I\"}]},{\"id\":\"79e4da36-f360-4435-82c8-960e9f78eb79\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"think there's not just one. I think these are all pieces to a bigger puzzle, and I think it's helpful for us as we sit and listen to understand fully.\"}]},{\"id\":\"346ce1a6-2886-460e-a6e7-1acb9f5b5e4b\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Treated this, did anyone intentionally use AI in a meeting where we're going to discuss AI? Um, I'm continuing to hear positive phrases from both people sitting at either end of the table in reference to AI, although I think they think that they're using neutral terms.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d07d793c-a86f-4755-8639-fb113075d85e\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, and I was just curious because this was a moment for us to be asked when we use AI, so I thought it was fair to ask was AI used for this. I just thought it was a fair question. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d1f97413-3f93-4a96-b4a5-a7ca06e33b64\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"No, it is. Yeah. Absolutely. That's what I'm trying to get\"}]},{\"id\":\"d7c9ef71-32d8-42e9-ab9c-8700a61e7ab2\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"at, right? Um-hum. It's OK. I'm just sort of calling out where,\"}]},{\"id\":\"872bc325-aa32-4473-9274-45607046d583\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Where we're at in the, in the rest of our time, right? So, and that's totally fine. Um, yeah, so, in fact, uh, speaking of maybe go back to what you, what you're put on the table there. Yeah. Um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"44bf6a96-a19d-43da-a2e5-0bf5669ae2a1\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"so. So. Anyone else, Pat, do you use AI intentionally? No. OK. Nope.\"}]},{\"id\":\"dab992b5-88a4-4a2f-bcae-4e7629084c99\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Nope.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b044fa62-790b-44bf-be2e-644c66d19284\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Excellent.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e956a6b4-8a52-4b14-946f-80633825b384\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Intentionally, no, but. Um-hum it's like you have no choice. And every single app that you have on your phone. Right. Has it on there. It's forced on us. Um-hum. Yes. Yes. And even when we, we click not interested, it still gets offered to us so often, even though we deny it when we don't want it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7c7b0651-e1a1-489e-b058-8307dfc9ddb3\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I won't even read the\"}]},{\"id\":\"a9aff9a4-36cd-47d2-832d-064bad6e242b\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"copilot response when I ask a question, a Google or a,\"}]},{\"id\":\"66340091-3058-403d-bf0f-a5ea8f8683e6\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Whatever Bing, whatever engine I\"}]},{\"id\":\"8700ae50-8e50-4f64-aacf-46d53818981c\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"use.\"}]},{\"id\":\"3f6c5711-41e9-460c-85e1-8c78e732f3c5\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Uh-huh.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d3b36c66-8483-4bb2-b984-51ee6e80c2e5\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If it gives me that AI, I won't read that because that was not generated by, I want to go to actual\"}]},{\"id\":\"a75592fc-6e3c-48f5-a4d7-8f9eaf3de063\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"sources.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e85f228a-2574-422b-97ce-f2775fd0fa8f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Just want to search it. Yeah. Yes.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7be04371-61a4-4029-afb8-ea831c21a9f6\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I didn't ask for you to tell me.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4300cb0c-d0ed-415c-b322-fbb3b2d363fd\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I, I, I think a point that I was trying to make earlier on is that AI happened to us. Um-hum. We weren't asked about it. We weren't given a choice. It, it was part of the package that comes. It's kind of like getting somebody hooked on a drug.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b1f90676-b762-4121-8261-5285e3819af0\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Uh, you get them started bit by bit, it fills in, you get, oh, hey, this is kind of handy, and you get to kind of liking that. And the more you use it, the more you kind of like it, the more you get hooked on it. Then the more data centers we have to build, and that's where I come from. I'm about the environment. So there you talk about the many aspects of AI. The data centers is the major aspect of AI that I'm concerned with right now, so.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5884a1ca-8530-465b-916c-6f4b3c427417\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That's all I have to say, evidently, uh, no, no, I mean, uh, see some of the AI centers are powering, they're using up enough energy to power 100,000 homes at a time, and there are, there are places that are being told, Lake Tahoe, for instance, 30% of their population is being told you have so.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c0eb724a-358d-447a-b0c0-ca523c9d14f5\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So much time and I think it's until the beginning of the year before you have to find some other source for your electricity because we're sending that to the data centers so it's humans against data centers it's humans the water, OK, and I'm gonna say this, everybody thinks that Opal Springs isn't.\"}]},{\"id\":\"59ed3e8b-d3bc-4310-83d1-fa2c51df3c4b\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Endless supply of water. It is not. It is glacier and snow melt and look at the mountains today. We can see that the glaciers are leaving the mountains. OK, but we've still got Opal Springs water. It's still bubbling up, so it's endless. No, it's not, folks. And where are they going to want to put data centers? They're going to want to put data centers where they can get the water.\"}]},{\"id\":\"513db2e7-3181-4606-9d4c-54364724fa3c\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And we have the river and cheap land, so we're gonna move out people out of rural areas and build data centers. The farmers are gonna have to move because they don't have the water and the farmers are going against.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ab867f14-9939-4148-b7d6-8850da865cb7\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right now already, so I don't see how anybody in this area could be for the production of data centers, and that's why I mentioned Nick Snead because it was mentioned that data centers are an option.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b3ece365-b192-4b0f-96ae-768f266c7633\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, the water usage issue can be resolved. Um\"}]},{\"id\":\"2a0f3259-0840-4455-b0a8-54dc2d3803ae\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"how many years from now? Yes. And how many tax breaks. It's,\"}]},{\"id\":\"33260714-b117-4560-9611-7db039df55ab\",\"interv