ver.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cea0d1b0-5266-4ef0-9557-dec282e4b0cb\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Or.\"}]},{\"id\":\"27f5e58a-d663-4d7d-b6ca-9267d4ee5b10\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"There's\"}]},{\"id\":\"b01d7ed4-ea3a-43e7-85af-ae4dbcb4f6ea\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, our land on the Yakama Nation, on the Pbum land, uh,\"}]},{\"id\":\"eef4e8f7-1be3-471c-a4cd-1a3a4430d744\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That is our sacred land and that's what we've gathered gathered our traditional foods from time immorial.\"}]},{\"id\":\"13a60cf3-2b5b-421f-8948-9db915ccec2e\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, along the Columbia River has always been a sacred place where we would gather and trade in.\"}]},{\"id\":\"804e78b3-d58e-4b52-a7ac-d874533d22d0\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um\"}]},{\"id\":\"466e0ff1-39ed-476d-9fdf-ee14898bdc34\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Our water is under attack, is how I feel. That's my concern. My concern is the next 7 generations, not just for my people, not just for indigenous people, but for all people. My concern is for, for your children, your grandchildren, your great great grandchildren. We are all humans here.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d6628fb3-93e7-4b33-8de0-f6faadb6183e\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And in our body percentage is pretty high of water. Water is life. Water is everything to my people. We, we start our ceremonials with water. We end our ceremonies with water. We don't look at water as a resource. We look at water as something that is alive.\"}]},{\"id\":\"224a2906-014b-4ae8-8ee0-125ad21390d7\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"We, we, we.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cc09c2b8-6493-4fe8-b52a-7d8ce63a72de\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Let me throw out a question. He was talking about closed loop system. Just\"}]},{\"id\":\"2f2c9ae3-ec06-4951-bb77-f578dba8c10c\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"hold on a second. Were you still, I, I want to. Yeah, yeah, no, go ahead. Finish your thought and then we'll.\"}]},{\"id\":\"bf8a9805-c722-4415-9be0-61baadcf3243\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, so along the Columbia River, even though, um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"84127303-b3ad-4ac4-9b67-730fb92a1a69\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You know, we weren't asked, our people weren't asked along the Columbia River Gorge and, and they're building them anyways, and, and our people are, are standing up against these things and.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d62a23dc-5aa9-487b-87eb-80f1e3033d12\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And it's to the point where like the land is under attack and.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b16eca59-ffae-48fb-889c-40987d3c7cf1\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It starts to heal hopefully.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2934ace0-46b7-424e-87d9-cf634b395c2f\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It starts to feel like we're not heard. We, that um that our beliefs and our religion and our way of life is, is not considered because.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b0b95b47-7c68-4567-91ef-5febc6abb10d\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Everybody, it's not everybody, but people are so.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1785c964-53be-4c99-a50f-5a64e6f72987\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Concentrated on taking from the earth and just raping it of.\"}]},{\"id\":\"af360905-264c-45db-aa93-e6d7c1fcfc71\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Of its resources that people like to call it. And for us, it's, it's very much alive. It's there's a love to this earth, there's a connection to this earth.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9b0c77b7-7884-43b7-9dd5-74e831d8f0ee\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And um, and I feel like as human beings, we should all have a connection to this earth. We are all connected to this earth and once we lose that, you know.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fdd6c823-cf50-4bce-b4ae-2ab98eb85f2b\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"We, we lose important values.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d34d294a-4882-40e7-9794-8099c9a05133\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The way we think and care for ourselves, it's, it's a big deal. We're all human and we're all connected to this earth and we should all care.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2f3f8d05-59fc-4c5b-81a0-da1e7962a2d6\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And not just think of it as resources.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e438c83d-2b8b-4f51-97b7-8da8068f1c27\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So what\"}]},{\"id\":\"4480edf2-d8c8-45ec-ad46-132e7b9831b9\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Out of curiosity. We're, I'm, now I'm worried about water. Sorry. Well, well, yeah,\"}]},{\"id\":\"b82fcc66-8302-42f8-a45d-49c1db42baa2\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"but I wanted to ask you, um, water usage is a very real concern. And, and I'm totally with you there. A closed, a closed loop, loop system like what you're talking about though, would, it's using, it's,\"}]},{\"id\":\"286250b8-37cf-466b-9532-7b77e0af2f9e\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Different kind. Using liquid cooling, but it's, uh, rather than using evaporation, uh, to, to cool it, uh, using larger radiators, I assume.\"}]},{\"id\":\"13c71f5f-875f-4c01-9a7f-3ab51443101f\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Uh,\"}]},{\"id\":\"73e6f848-4306-4cbc-be3a-52508313304f\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"it's the type of a system that they've created that has, it's a cooling tower basically, and it, it cools down the system. It just recirculates the water, and this is\"}]},{\"id\":\"423ae557-0af3-438b-a7ba-25a744b74f46\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"all a system they don't lose water through evaporation.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c30f3cb5-3443-4240-a72c-94ec22ebf9e8\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, they will lose water through evaporation, but they're trying to they're just trying to cool down the pipes that, that are containing the coolant.\"}]},{\"id\":\"56a1d6f2-be97-4454-997d-16dd3e02a653\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"In the meantime, so they're not taking as much water as the other ones. Uh, the other ones are using thousands of gallons a day, 1.6 or more terawatt of power per day to control these systems, and that's why I went into a whole different field and started designing the propulsion systems and stuff like that for ED Eviol, and then.\"}]},{\"id\":\"dbe1761e-4630-4a08-8d49-aedbcdb6b91d\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Eventually for database uh to make sure that they are off grid and powering themselves because they're not causing this issue to the environment that they're doing because I, I'm also Native American and my children are registered to the mountain, so we're, we, we see the same value as everyone else.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9f25121a-9b03-4d42-a26d-0c459c56cd32\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"that these are destroying, you know, these are, these are doing wrong instead of right, and AI is coming regardless of how we want it to do it or not. Shouldn't be on any type of tribal land if we don't want it. If, if, if, if they're forcing, there's ways to stop it and, and there's legal ways to stopping it, and you can prove that that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e6a34dab-b635-4686-adba-5a714c523ec3\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"These, if they leach into any type of water source, gone, gone, so you buy, you just wasted hundreds of millions of dollars coming in. Now you owe the whole community hundreds of millions of dollars to fix what you've done.\"}]},{\"id\":\"141a5d85-3965-411e-b815-71c8a99381e2\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But it's, it's a simple solution to, to it, and that's how you prevent them from coming back.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5a7d64ef-b39d-487b-ad2c-dbc2a0bfdf9c\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah because you, you, you, you have to be bold about it. You have to be because these are guys that are just gonna railroad and run you right over if you want it, they're, they're doing it all over.\"}]},{\"id\":\"66d33716-06c3-462e-9039-d97b1b90644c\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't wanna see any of this type of stuff happen. That's why I'm going in different on saying I can put this all into a closed loop system that doesn't do the damage that it's doing today.\"}]},{\"id\":\"88db7dff-2f24-42ff-abf0-13874fbad99a\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And it, it takes a lot of people standing up to say that we're done, we're done with this. We don't technically need AI. AI is infancy state right now, so you're not doing, I don't know if you guys have anybody here talked to any of the AI that's out there right now, co-pilot, Gemini, any. It's BS. It lies to you a lot. OK, I catch it on a daily basis. I caught it last night telling me why my one of my apps wasn't number one, OK? And it will tell you we are rigged.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2c99fa1a-2073-4627-bfb0-dde53bc387af\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Their their own AI will tell you that they are rigged for big corporate and that's it, right? So it, you have to be, you have to be willing to stand up and say this is enough is enough, we're done, you know. If you, if, if you wanna bring it here, show us that you're 100% contained and you don't, you won't do anything to, to harm what's around us or us together, you know, and then that, that solves it all. They either go ahead or they bring in a system that won't.\"}]},{\"id\":\"41617f65-c470-4e1a-87fa-e953d9fc2675\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And the corporations need to pay their own bills. I mean, if it's, if it's really a, a powerhouse of, of, uh, profitability, then they should be able to pay their own bills with that profit,\"}]},{\"id\":\"c29633df-8442-42bf-8cb1-28f5790d4c4b\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"right? Exactly.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9cc44808-de84-4443-9f55-ea1dd284ff99\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Exactly. See, and I, and, and, and, and I agree with, if they're going to take jobs, you need to be able to provide a way of, of,\"}]},{\"id\":\"91afb219-1e13-4990-a903-366aabea5244\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Building back that because you can't just take away jobs and call it that, that, that'll suck the money out of any state, but if they're not gonna be willing to train people of the jobs that they're taking away, then they don't belong in that area.\"}]},{\"id\":\"98b0b332-10f9-42ad-85ef-e419131252f6\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, let me, I'd like to ask you a question because, because you're familiar with the data centers in Prineville. Uh, I, I realize I'm shifting gears here. How many?\"}]},{\"id\":\"5755e239-2d5e-49b6-8d75-a0d12f002cc6\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"How large is the engineering staff? I'm not talking about the technicians who swap data, swap motherboards and CPUs and, and do cooling system repairs. How many software engineers, and hardware engineers do they have in Prineville? Oh, I don't think they have any. Boom. That's a concern I have.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0a729517-8568-45b5-928b-84b6ee48758e\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Because that's I mean, I don't know for sure, but that's not what they're designed to do, you know, they have, they have the technician. I mean there are a lot of jobs they've created 400 some odd jobs up there and, uh, well, meta is, but not at the data center, um, but they, they are not.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f77c7719-e9ef-4db0-b454-c92385b31912\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Software engineering jobs. They are. Right. Network management jobs. They are janitorial jobs. They are security jobs. They are food service jobs. They are, you know, all kinds of. Well, and that's different jobs, but\"}]},{\"id\":\"ac169b94-10fb-4e70-845b-156c81b8bc40\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"it's. That right there is my concern is that they. Yeah. They come in with a promise of, yeah, we're going to, we're going to supercharge your, your local economy. Um-hum. And, and we're going to sprinkle magic, magic IT bus, uh, dust all over, all over your town and, and suddenly you're going to,\"}]},{\"id\":\"9d948141-35a8-40cb-953a-f2f29301625a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Be rolling in cash. That's not how it works. They bring in a construction team to build the data center, and when they're done, then they roll out and they, they hire a few janitorial staff and a few, uh, technicians to swap out hard drives and motherboards.\"}]},{\"id\":\"adf81680-6834-4db1-8478-0eac8fa0897a\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, it's not really a few in, in our case, and I'm not speaking for all data centers,\"}]},{\"id\":\"3a5da07e-6038-41e5-a1d3-c6e5e6053b0d\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"but for data centers in Virginia.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d762503f-fa43-45f2-addf-e1120dfff217\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And England.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fdae01fc-267e-4e0a-9db3-20c520d1a85e\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I,\"}]},{\"id\":\"65ab9b4c-afb1-4cfb-8e69-1e92218280f9\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and I know for a fact that those data centers are, every single system in there is identical to the one right next to it, because even the computing, computing systems themselves are completely virtualized. So all they need is identical systems, and they can build all kinds of, all kinds of really cool magic stuff. But it's all, it's all going on within the systems. Um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"eb45b557-d153-4305-9777-98a46f61f8ff\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So they don't, all they need is somebody to swap out a bad motherboard and, and swap out hard\"}]},{\"id\":\"89a46920-510b-4be3-8fc9-b754ea1e59cb\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"drives.\"}]},{\"id\":\"334b2398-7a2e-43eb-bab7-a0da4b1e5a05\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So you're saying just a little bit above minimum wage jobs that they have brought with, with, uh, of course.\"}]},{\"id\":\"309b42df-f7b5-49de-82c2-e3b90e16f1fd\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, it's kind of like they use the resources and they'll give minimum wage jobs to people that needed jobs anyway, but what have they really brought to the community? I, I would. You know, have, have they brought higher wages? I would love to\"}]},{\"id\":\"21e73df5-e3b8-4071-be42-023954aec8de\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"see management be brought into town. Yeah. Well,\"}]},{\"id\":\"8f3b8e0d-9e72-4bc0-abcf-6cb56728389f\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"these are all the things that you guys. So before they even bring it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"8523ad87-006f-45ba-a402-2e02b55a289b\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, and, but that's You're\"}]},{\"id\":\"1a43d597-8303-4f67-b26f-d4432421fdda\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"saying you can't build here unless you,\"}]},{\"id\":\"923e6152-dcbc-4c08-ba87-04aa38104af2\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You provide a certain percentage of jobs here that are stable here\"}]},{\"id\":\"c60fd74b-1afb-4829-9229-2f6a81fe6396\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and. Yeah, but, but, but what we're hearing, I, I'm sorry, but I, I do listen to the news and I do read, but what we're hearing is there's too many times that they come in, the deal is done before the community even gets to talk about it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c61a176d-de74-45b0-87c8-4b43fe59c64e\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right. OK, so where's\"}]},{\"id\":\"89509804-7be5-4671-a747-83a84126bc1d\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"your, where's your regulation system then for that?\"}]},{\"id\":\"65dd29ff-7c4e-4add-b741-2c8c29035f19\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If, if you're gonna, if you're going to ask them to bring, you know, if you're going to allow it, then you have to set up the regulations as well. There's a lot of state regulation that doesn't happen, especially here in Oregon for some reason.\"}]},{\"id\":\"639180eb-8198-42dd-bf07-4d4f8b228ac4\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't, I don't. Well, but here, here's the point now we're, we're, we're retiring and here we're having to learn how to, one, what is the law in our state and, and how do we choose our.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ca3d89ca-2113-4058-aa40-bc5aa5ac6ab3\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Judges because we we're we're having to um fact check everything that we read nowadays it's getting to the point where you spend most of your day fact checking what the government and everybody else is telling you to the point where, uh, I thought the government was working.\"}]},{\"id\":\"396dede3-f5ad-4ba4-a237-9fbd7019c960\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Working for us, I thought our city government was working for us, and yes, we hired those people, but they promise you, you know, what they promise and then what you get are two different things. And if we haven't learned that by now, then we're not paying very good attention.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ee09d3f4-5008-4794-8426-a5a111da0ed9\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I could just say one thing, stop voting the same\"}]},{\"id\":\"8d91729b-b18b-42dd-97e5-5a51b1d90559\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"way.\"}]},{\"id\":\"41a011ee-7d34-4dfb-b658-081da5cefca4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, so before we go too far, Chris, you've joined us. You wanna do a little introduction and share your thoughts here? You haven't haven't had a chance to speak up on that topic.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e64c0788-6897-4f25-a513-c47cba55cd70\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, sure. How do I think AI might positively impact your community? First off, thanks for having me. Thanks for doing this. This was a wonderful idea. I hope that we get a lot more progress out of this. How do I think AI might positively impact our community? Well, I'm already seeing flights in it. I'm an entrepreneur, so what I'm seeing.\"}]},{\"id\":\"80e645fc-ac80-44e7-907a-54ab5f0dce0d\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Specifically in Gen Z, millennial and Gen X, because I'm seeing a lot of disruption and utilization and maximization early bird using the tools. As far as the manner in which it's used and the problem solving that it's used, we've transitioned from large language model, which was you telling AI a really, really lengthy, forever prompt. Now we've gone to agentic to AI and now it's something that you can actually just tell something and minimize your prompt.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2cc63e5f-992a-4bcd-a9c4-5324ef25ee59\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So on the entrepreneur side, this is definitely going to have some results. As far as rapid, I don't know, I, I couldn't tell you. I'm a little scared myself, um, so on the, on the impact, I'm seeing movement, Gen Z, millennial Gen X, a lot of good movement. Boomers, what I'm seeing on the boomer side, fact checking is very real. I'm seeing a lot, not a lot, but the minimal amount that I'm seeing of boomers using it, I'm seeing them utilize it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d3dd1fa9-c5b7-40b2-a449-f4a9b4fe5802\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"To quickly fact check things as opposed to sifting Google, if that makes any sense. Um, what worries me, the biggest things that worry me is the before and after EPA impacts. What were they before these data centers came? What are they right now? What are they forecasting? What resources are we talking about using as far as water and electricity? Those seem to be the top two commodities that are discussed, and those have me deeply alarmed. Now the\"}]},{\"id\":\"8c65f465-f5f8-4408-adb5-e511d4677d87\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The other thing that has me worried is this is such a hot topic that there's a lot of, it's almost like you cannot keep up. Entrepreneurs don't move at the speed of government, we move at the speed of business. But with everything that's going on, it really feels like even us, we just cannot keep up with everything that is going on. And I think to his point, yes, the burden of regulation now falls on us. There's a bunch of high profile.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9291c674-5c03-4c4c-8c6e-41f5e4e8bd80\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"entrepreneurs who are obviously making a disruption to make some money and, and that's just part of the game that's the nature of the beast. But what I'm learning and seeing unfold is that burden of regulation definitely falls on us and it will be probably like pulling teeth with our leaders. I'm not a political guy. I'm just an entrepreneur, but what I'm learning with all of this, this disruption, this whole thing is at a magnitude where it's.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5e245e86-d298-423a-99ab-f7444417b0c3\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It's bleeding in the indigenous. It has politician levels. It has electricity. It has water. This is an opportunity for us to gather together, have back and forth, and there's gonna be probably some moments where it's like ripping off a band-aid. It's gonna feel really hurt in the beginning, but the end goal is what I'm after. That's what I'm after. So I'm after how do we maximize this wonderful tool with minimal.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fde275b3-c38c-4bf6-a016-250565c1172e\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The other thing that really worries me is the difference between understanding what a true data center is and what a super data campus is. There's some very big differences between the two, and, and, and I'm seeing a lot of generalized terms that have me alarmed from both red and blue side generalizing, but I think that's where these community momentum meetings is gonna be the tool that gets all of the information out there.\"}]},{\"id\":\"72a61601-804a-47f6-9440-88bc6c0ba3ef\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"To your point, they also include a micro data set as well. Yes.\"}]},{\"id\":\"82070d3d-682f-4287-a050-3b860598d269\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The little housing ones.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7e2ee333-0e6c-4426-bf4f-65732f754f93\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right, and they're, they are loop systems. They're, they're, those are the ones that I would say would be OK for central,\"}]},{\"id\":\"1725fa1b-a9fa-49c7-b94f-32242ac2ab2a\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Or the center of the mall.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e955e774-eac1-4d7b-99a2-76849d1bffb0\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Box miner had a good, good insight, but they were gonna take the same water and not as in the data and not OK for the mine. It wasn't gonna happen. The same thing with power and the people were just already were those data campuses. Well it was box miner is is would would have been in the micro category.\"}]},{\"id\":\"64b610b3-bcde-426d-958a-506d37b65f69\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Not a campus and not a data center.\"}]},{\"id\":\"65a6d70d-0d8b-458c-bc34-68420898b94e\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So it\"}]},{\"id\":\"8873045d-728c-405c-ad6f-1bf7e42f0683\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Their setup was a little bit different when I looked at everything that he was offering and and saying just it kinda.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0cc4a806-7e47-4d55-ba23-ea5ceec51745\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It scares a lot of people. AI scares a lot of people right off the bat. I'm also an entreprene.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4506b314-9de5-4ee6-ad93-593e4c94d724\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Been in the game for a while, but mine are more construction based.\"}]},{\"id\":\"bf62ac87-83e9-4e90-afaa-0791a527085b\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Did this turn?\"}]},{\"id\":\"c3709aa8-e811-40d4-be85-661a9fc82a01\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"No, so, uh, I've always been like I'm not political, so to say. I'm just saying\"}]},{\"id\":\"00941dd9-d2fa-4dcb-bd25-068ef81793ed\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"you're plugged in but\"}]},{\"id\":\"396d9fe4-59ae-43b0-9b70-0f72d8ea5e5b\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"not really right. So, so, so my, my whole thing is if, if you don't, if you don't like what's happening, get involved, get involved or, or, or make a change, you know, and, and, and that's how you, that's how you, you, you, you make it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"767a7869-30c9-4533-a281-627091220b23\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Sounds like we're\"}]},{\"id\":\"93329f82-f15c-432d-9577-81dc40f624ec\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"in the same\"}]},{\"id\":\"592f8aac-51d3-4920-9c0c-57f8d8582868\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"mind, right?\"}]},{\"id\":\"4ce347b5-a9d3-46db-be50-511d4c4b5e6a\",\"inter