rn it off, you know, and, and when you're throwing data out there and you're not protecting yourself, it, it, it can, it's all exposed. I\"}]},{\"id\":\"2b533ac8-fec0-4b03-be1f-41130125b76f\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"mean, and to his point, I don't, I, I work in the industry. I don't have a Lexus.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c9515a8f-272f-4ab5-9690-d31ec39ff33e\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"No, I, I\"}]},{\"id\":\"649befed-9e5b-4ade-b15b-9cfd90d8f33a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"don't want Bezos to listen to my.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f489cd52-d8e0-4eeb-a3ca-39f997ff7d68\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"What's, what's going on in my house.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1e7b93db-2a3f-4463-9272-da834ff1fcd3\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, see, I, I, I think we pretty much tried to do away with as many of those things as we possibly could, you know.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0611bc7b-6c5b-476b-a3bc-5a4a66b26349\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Search queries, that's great. I got, I got the information right where I needed it, right, boom. But,\"}]},{\"id\":\"9ac0fe82-5757-4288-9025-88fe2161e81b\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, I don't, I don't\"}]},{\"id\":\"fa5c3d8e-95f0-4c04-bd67-451395877498\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Need Zuckerberg listening to conversations between my wife and my, myself.\"}]},{\"id\":\"39c468ef-db6d-482c-8855-37ec6e41dcd1\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And if you do, if you do want to keep something proprietary to you and you're, and you're working with a different AI agent, you need to tell it. This is proprietary to me and my company. It will, it will no longer allow any conversation to lead past that point. The only people that can see it is the developer.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b68e05aa-8397-4bd1-acb3-cfde40559090\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[