ned it up, but a lot of them haven't, so there's still a lot of, if you're building on these sites, make sure that you're closing that that that loop in the back end, otherwise they'll leave it open and somebody can attack you. It happens.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b1ff82dc-bca6-4b88-93be-8a576521ebcf\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Something that she was saying earlier that that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"8884914c-159f-4320-b7a6-724af36327c3\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Made me think that was what she was talking about, um, is that,\"}]},{\"id\":\"b9c12c9a-580f-4983-8676-77cb3d561a10\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"There, there are artists, there are writers, there are uh people who who make their make their living on what they create. Whether it's whether it's in word form, or or art form or whatnot. Uh, AI is collecting all this information, and, and taking samples of all of that. And you could literally make a movie, uh, make a full blown motion picture.\"}]},{\"id\":\"100a6567-0062-48c5-bb5e-0a69bb2e9fe1\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Without having to, uh Hire. Without having to hire a staff. Um-hum. Uh, so, you know, that. That, yeah. Yeah, that, that to me is a, is a concern.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0151762a-c7e2-4a12-ad70-e5a46ac7fcf1\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yes, Dave.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d6702074-0a45-4854-82a2-390f8d1cbb82\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Oh, Excellent. 200. I'm sorry. I'm,\"}]},{\"id\":\"d4220c8b-592b-412c-a588-34e87a77c691\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm sorry, Dave. I, I can't do that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"88b678b1-3626-4715-a28e-df66b60be90b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Open the pod bay door, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"60adb559-f63c-4883-a6a4-215d19938911\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Thank you very much. I think this is here,\"}]},{\"id\":\"6